title: >-
  SBMPMS-observability: MATLAB codes for "Melnikov-Based Observability
  Breakdown in Singular Bilinear Periodic Matrix Differential Systems"

abstract: >-
  This repository contains the MATLAB implementation, verified numerical
  outputs, and publication-quality figures for the paper "Melnikov-Based
  Observability Breakdown in Singular Bilinear Periodic Matrix Differential
  Systems" (submitted to Chaos, Solitons and Fractals, Elsevier, May 2026).
  Key results: observability breakdown threshold eps_dagger = 0.118,
  controllability threshold eps_star = 0.170, controllability-observability
  gap = 30.59% (exact, MATLAB verified), threshold stable on [0.114, 0.123]
  across a tenfold tolerance range, Kronecker-free O(Nn^3) algorithm with
  105800x speedup at n=50.

version: 2.0.0
