  - Melnikov perturbation
  - observability breakdown
  - observability phase transition
  - codimension-one rank bifurcation
  - blind control regime
  - Kalman-Hewer equivalence
  - observability Gramian expansion
  - controllability-observability duality
  - Kronecker-free computation
  - chemical reaction networks
  - singular descriptor systems
  - MATLAB
  - nonlinear dynamics
  - Chaos Solitons and Fractals

